21:08.977 --> 21:10.896
-No two paths
-No two paths

21:10.979 --> 21:12.731
-Are the same
-Are the same

21:12.814 --> 21:14.691
No two paths

21:14.775 --> 21:17.778
No two paths are the same

21:18.779 --> 21:20.280
I gotta go find Red.

21:23.700 --> 21:25.702
Don't worry. That was just a oner.

21:31.124 --> 21:32.459
Today has been a day.

21:33.126 --> 21:35.546
The solar panels keep shorting.

21:35.629 --> 21:38.423
Jar six was a bust.
Nothing's eating plastic.

21:38.507 --> 21:41.885
I don't know how I'm gonna do
more than I'm already doing.

21:44.263 --> 21:47.975
Can you please make one thing easy
and take your medicine?

21:49.142 --> 21:51.895
You know I don't have time
for whatever this is.

21:53.856 --> 21:55.983
Okay, fine.

21:57.985 --> 21:59.027
What now?

22:01.363 --> 22:02.865
I guess you're kinda cute.

22:05.951 --> 22:07.870
It feels good to slow down, huh?

22:12.791 --> 22:15.419
What, really? Now you're gonna take it?

22:16.086 --> 22:17.754
You just wanted a cuddle.

22:27.598 --> 22:28.682
Open up.

22:31.101 --> 22:32.644
That's my dog.

22:33.937 --> 22:36.440
I still can't believe
I wasted a block of cheese on you.

22:36.523 --> 22:38.066
You owe me some cheddar.

22:42.237 --> 22:44.448
Red, how are you doing?

22:44.531 --> 22:47.951
Bad. I'm doing very bad.

22:48.035 --> 22:49.703
Red, I'm sorry.

22:49.786 --> 22:54.416
I really wanted you to try meditation
because it works so well for me, and--

22:54.499 --> 22:56.710
and I think it could work for you.

22:56.793 --> 23:00.756
But it has to be your way, not mine.

23:00.839 --> 23:05.135
So if you ever want help finding that,
I'm here.

23:05.219 --> 23:07.054
I appreciate that, Mokey.

23:07.137 --> 23:11.308
But I don't think meditation is for me.

23:11.391 --> 23:15.521
I'm an action Fraggle.
That's how I clear my head.

23:15.604 --> 23:18.398
I like to dive headfirst, yell "whoopee,"

23:18.482 --> 23:23.028
and then hit that water
and let everything disappear.

23:23.111 --> 23:25.489
That sounds peaceful.

23:25.572 --> 23:26.573
It is.

23:26.657 --> 23:30.786
I love the water weaving through
my pigtails as I swirl in the currents.

23:30.869 --> 23:32.579
Yes.

23:32.663 --> 23:35.249
It feels like a warm hug.

23:35.332 --> 23:37.751
Huge hug fan over here.

23:53.308 --> 23:56.562
There's nothing better than this.

23:56.645 --> 23:57.980
Mind if I join you?

23:58.063 --> 23:59.982
I was hoping you would.

24:16.665 --> 24:19.585
Mokey, this is amazing.

24:19.668 --> 24:21.962
I totally feel like myself again.

24:22.713 --> 24:25.382
Red, I am so proud of you--

24:25.465 --> 24:27.092
I'm still in the zone.

24:27.176 --> 24:28.552
Sorry. Sorry.
